{"type": "article", "id": 9810, "title": "作为一家烤肉店，它在店外挂了3000块木炭", "description": "这种店铺装饰方式颇有气势。", "date": "2015-05-21T08:34:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 10410, "name": "烤肉店"}, {"id": 10411, "name": "木炭"}, {"id": 3000, "name": "店铺设计"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 70, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607105706tVK1U3mHiMTPAEe8.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t为了突出“碳烤”的概念，这家日本烤肉店把 3000 块木炭请进了屋。近日， <a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/design/supermaniac-inc-dining-nen-restaurant-japan-05-19-2015/\" target=\"_blank\">designboom 网站贴出了这家餐厅的图片</a>，乍看起来，光线将木炭照的隐隐发亮，像是个什么会所。餐厅名叫“炭焼 DINING nen ”，设计是由<a href=\"http://www.supermaniac.ne.jp\" target=\"_blank\">日本的设计事务所 supermaniac </a>完成的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071057013fjuRwdraeEpH1L4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t烧烤店的入口长这样。其实在餐厅里，设计师放入了不少的小镜子，制造了视觉上层层叠叠的效果。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071057021fRzA2synZqP3J0G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t远远望去，真的不是个会所吗？\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105702SxMcibZmO74k1Je3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t木炭的细节，光线是从下部打上来的，这得费不少电吧？\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105703D7jRiT4wWn0eSUzy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t走进屋内，座位长这样。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105703oEyQ3njHhXTmlzVf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t靠墙桌，餐厅的内墙也有木炭装饰，有点现代和传统相结合的意思。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105704RQu71K0jLT4q8sw2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t菊花残，满地伤……设计师说他们采用了菊花的意象。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105704bsoNxH9JljtUhZV2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t多人桌，皮座。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105705sY2QNlgrwzH5kcyo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>supermaniac </span>设计事务所位于东京，专注于店铺设计，他们有不少的客户，比如下面这几个：<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105705EWoyg0i9jklTxJvd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<span>Omnibus O</span>ffice\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607105705sZNdfQX4i3gj8GVS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tKEY COFFEE\r\n</p>\r\n<em>题图来源：designboom</em>\n\n\n"}